import React from 'react'
import './footer.css'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <footer className="footer">
      <Container>
        <Row>
          <Col lg = "4" ></Col>
          <Col lg = "4" ></Col>
          <Col lg = "4" ></Col>
          <Col lg = "4" ></Col>

        </Row>
      </Container>
    </footer>
  )
}

export default Footer
